          Contact Support form, Free Inspection form, or interact with our
          website:
        </p>

        <div
          class="not-prose overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-gray-200 mb-8"
        >
          <table class="min-w-full divide-y divide-gray-200 text-sm">
            <thead class="bg-gray-50">
              <tr>
                <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700"
                  >Category</th
                >
                <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700"
                  >Data Elements</th
                >
                <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700"
                  >Source</th
                >
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="bg-white divide-y divide-gray-100">
              <tr>
                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-gray-800">Identifiers</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-600"
                  >First name, last name, email address, phone number</td
                >
                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-500">You (form submission)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-gray-50">
                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-gray-800"
                  >Property Data</td
                >
                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-600"
                  >Property address, city, state, zip code, country</td
                >
                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-500">You (inspection form)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-gray-800"
                  >Insurance Information</td
                >
                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-600"
                  >Whether the property has active insurance (yes/no only ‚Äî no
                  policy numbers)</td
                >
                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-500">You (inspection form)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-gray-50">
                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-gray-800"
                  >Communications</td
                >
                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-600"
                  >Message content, subject/service type, SMS consent preference</td
                >
                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-500">You (form submission)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-gray-800"
                  >Technical / Internet Activity</td
                >
                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-600"
                  >IP address, browser User-Agent string, form submission
                  timestamp, spam score (internal)</td
                >
                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-500">Automatically collected</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-gray-50">
                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-gray-800"
