            special category data under TDPSA or GDPR is collected.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ 2. PURPOSE ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ -->
        <h2 id="purpose" class="scroll-mt-20">
          2. Why We Collect This Data (Purpose of Processing)
        </h2>
