        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Scheduling free inspections</strong> ‚Äî To contact you and schedule
            a property assessment at your request.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Responding to support inquiries</strong> ‚Äî To answer your questions
            about our services, insurance claims, or restoration projects.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>SMS communications</strong> ‚Äî Only if you explicitly opt in. Used
            to send appointment reminders and status updates.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Fraud and spam prevention</strong> ‚Äî IP addresses and User-Agent
            strings are used to detect bots and prevent abuse (legitimate interest).
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Website analytics</strong> ‚Äî Aggregate, anonymized data via Google
            Analytics 4 to improve our website performance.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Legal compliance</strong> ‚Äî To meet our obligations under Texas
            law, TDPSA, and any applicable regulatory requirements.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          <strong>Legal basis (TDPSA/GDPR):</strong> Primarily <em
            >contract performance</em
          > (responding to your service request) and <em>legitimate interest</em
          > (fraud prevention, security). Consent is obtained for SMS notifications
          and optional analytics.
        </p>

