                  >Transactional email delivery (admin notifications)</td
                >
                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-600"
                  >Name, email, message content (admin copy only)</td
                >
                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-500">See provider's policy</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-gray-50">
                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-gray-800"
                  >Google Analytics 4</td
                >
                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-600"
                  >Website analytics (if enabled)</td
                >
                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-600"
