                >
                <td class="px-4 py-3"
                  ><a
                    href="https://policies.google.com/privacy"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener"
                    class="text-teal-600 hover:underline"
                    >policies.google.com/privacy</a
                  ></td
                >
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-gray-800"
                  >Insurance Adjusters / Sub-contractors</td
                >
                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-600"
                  >Service delivery (only when authorized by you)</td
                >
                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-600"
                  >Name, phone, property address, insurance status</td
                >
                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-500"
                  >Shared only under NDA / authorization</td
                >
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <p>
          We do not share your data with data brokers, advertising networks, or
          third-party marketers. We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal
          information.
        </p>

        <!-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ 4. RETENTION ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ -->
        <h2 id="retention" class="scroll-mt-20">4. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          We retain your personal data only as long as necessary for the
          purposes described above:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Contact & Appointment records:</strong> 3 years from last interaction,
            then securely deleted.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Spam/rate-limiting logs (IP addresses):</strong> 90 days, then
            automatically purged.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Email records:</strong> 2 years (in our email system), aligned
            with transactional record requirements.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Analytics data (Google Analytics 4):</strong> 14 months (Google's
            default retention).
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Legal obligations:</strong> If required by Texas law or a legal
            proceeding, records may be retained longer.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          You may request early deletion of your data at any time. See <a
            href="#your-rights">Section 5</a
          > for instructions.
        </p>

        <!-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ 5. YOUR RIGHTS ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ -->
