        </h2>
        <p>
          Under the <strong>Texas Data Privacy and Security Act (TDPSA)</strong
          >, Texas residents have the following rights. We will respond to all
          verified requests within <strong>45 days</strong> (extendable by 45 days
          with notice):
        </p>

        <div class="not-prose space-y-3 mb-8">
          {
            [
              {
                icon: "üëÅÔ∏è",
                title: "Right to Access",
                desc: "Request a copy of the personal data we hold about you, in a portable, machine-readable format (CSV/JSON).",
              },
              {
                icon: "‚úèÔ∏è",
                title: "Right to Correction",
                desc: "Request correction of inaccurate personal data we maintain about you.",
              },
              {
                icon: "üóëÔ∏è",
                title: "Right to Deletion",
                desc: "Request that we delete your personal data, subject to legal retention obligations.",
              },
              {
                icon: "üì¶",
                title: "Right to Portability",
                desc: "Receive your data in a structured, commonly used format (CSV or JSON).",
              },
              {
                icon: "üö´",
                title: "Right to Opt-Out",
                desc: "Opt out of the sale or sharing of personal data for targeted advertising (we do not sell data, but you may still submit this request).",
              },
              {
                icon: "‚öñÔ∏è",
                title: "Right to Appeal",
                desc: "If we deny your request, you may appeal. If still denied, you may file a complaint with the Texas Attorney General.",
              },
            ].map((right) => (
              <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border border-gray-200">
                <div class="text-2xl shrink-0">{right.icon}</div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-navy text-sm">{right.title}</p>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-0.5">{right.desc}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>

        <div
          class="not-prose bg-teal-50 border border-teal-200 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8"
        >
          <p class="font-bold text-teal-800 mb-2">üìã How to Submit a Request</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-teal-700 mb-4">
            Submit your Data Subject Access Request (DSAR) via any of these
            methods:
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
            <a
              href="/privacy-request"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-teal-600 text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-teal-700 transition-colors"
